version_description: I hope you like it. You'll use capo on the 3rd fret. Here is the link of the video: https://youtu.be/1iSd_wTuA3U.
Other versions do not include the tabbed out parts of the saxophone solo and the outro, which seems to be essential to a song leaning heavily on the late Clarence Clemons.

version_description: This is a personal mashup of Harry Style's Sign of the Times and Lady Gaga's Million Reasons. Simple basic chords, it's mainly SOTT with a bit of million reasons slotted in. They both have similar chord progressions so I thought they would sound good together. Still working on it and improving. LMK what you think?

The other versions of this song are simplified, but this version is the real chords you hear in the studio version. The chords are in the same key as the song, but you can use capo to make it easier to play on guitar.
This is the only version for this song off the Joanne album.
It's the first original by me.
